    "intro": {
        "scroll_speed": 40,
        "scroll_offset": 225,
        "stop": 2325,
        "scrolling_text": {
            "0": {
                "text": "You are dead.",
                "y": 960,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "1": {
                "text": "You died poor and alone.",
                "y": 990,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "2": {
                "text": "Without a proper burial,",
                "y": 1020,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "3": {
                "text": "you were denied entrance to the underworld",
                "y": 1050,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "4": {
                "text": "and forced to roam the Earth as a ghost",
                "y": 1080,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "5": {
                "text": "for eternity.",
                "y": 1110,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "6": {
                "text": "As time went on, you began to hunger for revenge.",
                "y": 1210,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "7": {
                "text": "Revenge against all who wronged you:",
                "y": 1240,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "8": {
                "text": "those who never helped you up,",
                "y": 1270,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "9": {
                "text": "those who only helped you down,",
                "y": 1300,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "10": {
                "text": "and those who taught you that nothing mattered but greed,",
                "y": 1330,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "11": {
                "text": "the ghosts of your past life.",
                "y": 1360,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "12": {
                "text": "You wanted retribution.",
                "y": 1460,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "13": {
                "text": "But as a ghost you are unable to touch the living,",
                "y": 1490,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "14": {
                "text": "so you turned your sights to the main thing",
                "y": 1520,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "15": {
                "text": "that had been denied from you: gold.",
                "y": 1550,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "16": {
                "text": "However, as a ghost, you can not be near",
                "y": 1580,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "17": {
                "text": "any gold that has been seen by the living.",
                "y": 1610,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "18": {
                "text": "You began to venture into old mining shafts.",
                "y": 1710,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "19": {
                "text": "Then, you found an abandoned gold mine.",
                "y": 1740,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "20": {
                "text": "You stopped your exploration",
                "y": 1770,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "21": {
                "text": "and vowed to never leave the mine",
                "y": 1800,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "22": {
                "text": "until you had taken all of its gold.",
                "y": 1830,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "23": {
                "text": "As you started clearing the mine, it grew unstable.",
                "y": 1930,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "24": {
                "text": "And the longer you were the mine,",
                "y": 1960,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "25": {
                "text": "the more unstable it became.",
                "y": 1990,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "26": {
                "text": "But this does not bother you.",
                "y": 2090,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "27": {
                "text": "As shafts collapse, they reveal hidden pockets gold.",
                "y": 2120,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "28": {
                "text": "However, the shafts also contain old mining explosives",
                "y": 2150,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "29": {
                "text": "which were never disarmed and",
                "y": 2180,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "30": {
                "text": "explode when they came in contact with the ground.",
                "y": 2210,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "31": {
                "text": "Undeterred, you continue to stay in the mine,",
                "y": 2310,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "32": {
                "text": "with the futile task of hunting",
                "y": 2340,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "33": {
                "text": "the endless gold.",
                "y": 2370,
                "font": "h4"
            },
            "34": {
                "text": "Ghosts & Gold",
                "y": 2500,
                "font": "h1"
            },
            "35": {
                "text": "A game by: LelsersLasers",
                "y": 2590,
                "font": "h3"
            }
        },
